alteration /ˌɔːltəˈreɪʃən/

(alterations) 

1. N-COUNT An alteration is a change in or to something. 改动 

例： Making some simple alterations to your diet will make you feel fitter. 对你的饮食做一些简单的改变会使你感觉更健康。 

2. N-UNCOUNT The alteration of something is the process of changing it. 改变 

例： Her jacket was at the boutique waiting for alteration. 她的夹克在服装精品店里等待修改。

